Load survey data, phenotype data, ethnicity data.

Source: R/load_data.R
load_data.Rd

Load survey data, phenotype data, ethnicity data.

load_data(survey_path, ethnicity_path, pheno_path, trait_name, default_cohorts)

Arguments

survey_path

Path to survey file.
ethnicity_path

Path to ethnicity data directory.
pheno_path

Path to phenotypes data directory.
trait_name

Name of the trait.
default_cohorts

Default ethnicity cohorts.

Value

Prepared data.
